</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Mi&s;s RICHLAND.</SPEAKER>
<P>Sir, I &s;hould be ungrateful not to be plea&s;ed with
any thing that comes recommended by you.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>CROAKER.</SPEAKER>
<P>How, boy, could you de&s;ire a finer opening?
Why don't you begin, I &s;ay? <STAGE>(To Leont.)</STAGE></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>LEONTINE.</SPEAKER>
<P>'Tis true, madam, my father, madam, has &s;ome
