you one that loves you; one who&s;e whole hap|pine&s;s
is all in you.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<PB N="31" REF="37">
<SPEAKER>Mi&s;s RICHLAND.</SPEAKER>
<P>I never had any doubts of your regard, Sir; and
