</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Mi&s;s RICHLAND.</SPEAKER>
<P>If I could flatter my&s;elf, you thought as you
&s;peak, Sir&mdash;</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>LEONTINE.</SPEAKER>
<P>Doubt my &s;incerity, madam? By your dear &s;elf
