</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>CROAKER.</SPEAKER>
<P>Well, well, no more que&s;tions about it.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>LEONTINE.</SPEAKER>
<P>A&s;k the &s;ick, if they long for health? a&s;k mi&s;ers,
