</SP>
<SP>
<PB N="34" REF="40">
<SPEAKER>LEONTINE.</SPEAKER>
<P>But, Sir, I mu&s;t beg leave to in&s;i&s;t&mdash;</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>CROAKER.</SPEAKER>
<P>Get off, you puppy, or I'll beg leave to in&s;i&s;t
