</SP>
<STAGE>Enter FRENCH SERVANT.</STAGE>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>SERVANT.</SPEAKER>
<P>An expre&s;&s;e from Mon&s;ieur Lofty. He vil be
vait upon your honour's in&s;trammant. He be only
